Text.Value: Chk. Overheated grappling, that wastefully eats into time better spent resting our muscles.
You've read this all wrong. I'm not interested, Lae'zel.
Ever since we shared each others' flesh, I've caught you looking at me with lidded eyes.
And either like a coward or a fool, you tremble.
Perhaps the parasite has weakened you. Or perhaps - perhaps you still long for my taste.
Have the curiosities of this land muddled your head? Bah - at least you are choosing to lay with me instead of one of them.
On second thought, I'd rather be alone tonight.
And you've never strangled a Berbalang with your bare hands.
Shouldn't we enjoy all the sensations of Faerûn while we are here?
Besides, I can't deny the lure of your taste. Sweet, yes, but also bitter as ginger.
You've never done it before, have you?
It is foolish of me. I promise I shall stop.
I remember your heartbeat from before. Quick, light, like a frightened rabbit.
Very well. I will claim you once you have taken to rest.
I have been hoping we could spend the night together again.
Enough! I have given you my word. Do not be late.
Tempt me.
You're free to be with who you choose, but I hope you'll choose me.
Deep down, you like me more than anyone else here.
Just when my tongue was craving a second sample.
Why would a lesser act spark greater desire in you?
I want to press my head to your chest and feel the war drum of your heart.
I did not say it was unwelcome. Should a warrior not enjoy the flattery of her admirers?
The sex gets better the more experience you have with someone.
Yes. I have the pick of Faerûn's litter, though all I see are runts. They are the rule; you are the exception.
You are exceptional amongst our pack. You are clearly their leader, and they look to you for guidance. That, I admire.
I look forward to it dearly.
I never promised more than a night - though I can't deny the lure of your taste. Sweet, yes, but also bitter as ginger.
Like the shield-bearer and pikeman must train to march their formation in tandem.
Only if you promise to stick around for a cuddle afterwards.
Yes. Good.
I think you're mistaken, I've been having no such thoughts.
Good.
Chk - to think you'd starve yourself while gazing at a feast luscious as this.
I'll keep your request in mind. Perform well, and perhaps I'll consider it.

Synopsis: Player approaches Lae'zel to enjoy a second night of romance, which will be implied offscreen. This could either trigger at the party if the player already slept with Lae'zel, or any other time between her act 1 and 2 romance scenes. To set the feeling of the sexual relationship becoming a regular thing.
